  "comments": "<p><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/63c69f472e9b9.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/63c69f472e9b9.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a> P109a, signature Amarananda Jayawardena<br>Jayawardena was governor of the Bank of Sri Lanka from November 15th., 1995 until June 30th., 2004<br><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/63c69fc374d02.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/63c69fc374d02.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a> P109a, signature Chandrika Bandaranika Kumaratunga<br>Kumaratunga was Minister of Finance of Sri Lanka from September 30th., 1994 until December 5th., 2001</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Under backlight the security strip can be read. It has “CENTRAL BANK OF SRI LANKA RUPEES TWENTY” repeated on it:</p><p><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67b271ad3a16e.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67b271ad3a16e.jpg\"></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>UV activity at 365nm:<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67b271c8d1ded.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67b271c8d1ded.jpg\"></a> &nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/67b271d0ab6de.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/67b271d0ab6de.jpg\"></a><br><br>© Brandon Bertolli</p>",
